artists/brandi-carlile">布兰迪·卡莱尔</a>。 “但是写作真有趣。我必须把自己知道的东西带到桌子上，因为我是一个乡下女孩。所以我必须说，“不，不，不，不，让我给你看一些乡村歌曲。&#39;” </p><figure id="attachment_3836414" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3836414" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3836414" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan-2025-grammys@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan-2025-grammys@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan-2025-grammys@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan-2025-grammys@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan-2025-grammys@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan-2025-grammys@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/chappell-roan-2025-grammys@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3836414" class="wp-caption-text">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）在2025 Grammys演出。图片来源：克里斯托弗·波尔克/广告牌通过盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>在其他查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）新闻中，本月早些时候，歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-chappell-roans-best-new-artist-acceptance-speech-demands-record-labels-treat-their-artists-as-valuable-employees-3833896">在第67届格莱美奖上使用最好的新艺术家演讲来瞄准唱片公司</a>，并分享她过去作为苦苦挣扎的新艺术家的经验，成为头条新闻。</p><p>在此之前，歌手的“祝你好运，宝贝！”<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024-3817596">被称为<em>NME</em> 2024年的最佳歌曲</a>。 “祝你好运，宝贝！&#39;，罗恩（Roan）开始写一首&#39;大型幻想流行歌曲&#39;。这是一个不合格的成功：在巧妙地坚持合成的流行音乐中，罗恩为迫切试图否认自己的酷儿的人提供了家庭真相。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-reveals-plumber-version-of-new-single-the-giver-3841347">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）帖子揭示了新单曲“送礼者”的“水管工”版本</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 “哈利·波特”：约翰·利特哥（John Lithgow）确认扮演HBO系列中的邓布利多https://www.nme.com/news/tv/harry-potter-potter-john-lithgow-confirms-casting-casting-as-dumbledore-in-hbo-series-hbo-series-3841333？ _source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = harry-potter-john-lithgow-confirms-confirms-confirms-casting-as as Dumbledore-in-Hbo-in-Hbo系列Surej SinghWed, 26 Feb 2025 03:37:08 +0000 NewsTV NewsHarry Potter https://www.nme.com/?p=3841333 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这将在我一生的最后一章中定义我……我在包装派对上大约87岁”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/harry-potter-john-lithgow-confirms-casting-as-dumbledore-in-hbo-series-3841333">“哈利·波特”帖子：约翰·利特哥（John Lithgow）确认铸造为HBO系列中的邓布利多（Dumbledore），</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>演员约翰·利特哥（John Lithgow）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">HBO</a>即将推出的《哈利·波特》（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/harry-potter"><em>Harry Potter）</em></a>的电视改编中证实了他的演员阵容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-white-lotus-season-3-review-3836677">“白莲花”第三季评论：不可抗拒的假期肥皂仍然是电视最重要的目的地</a></strong></li></ul><p>据报道，据报道，美国演员约翰·利特哥（John Lithgow）因霍格沃茨（Hogwarts）的校长<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/harry-potter-tv-series-reportedly-eyeing-john-lithgow-as-dumbledore-3837545">阿不思（Albus Dumbledore）的角色</a>和霍博（HBO）即将举行的电视连续剧中名义上的哈利·波特（Harry Potter）的指导人物而被关注。</p><p>根据利斯高（Lithgow）的说法，他在与<a href="https://screenrant.com/harry-potter-show-john-lithgow-dumbledore-casting-confirmed/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Screen Rant</em></a>的聊天中 - 他接受了这一提议，并将在该系列中担任标志性向导。这将标志着特许经营历史上的第一次，该角色是由非英国或爱尔兰演员扮演的。 </p><figure id="attachment_3841343" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841343" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841343" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/john-lithgow@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841343" class="wp-caption-text">约翰·利特哥（John Lithgow）。图片来源：克里斯托弗·波尔克（Christopher Polk）/综艺</figcaption></figure><p>利特哥在谈到他的<em>演员</em>时说：“好吧，这让我感到惊讶。我刚刚在圣丹斯电影节上打了电话，这是另一部电影，这并不是一个容易的决定，因为我恐怕要定义我的一生的最后一章。”</p><p>利斯高继续：“但是我很兴奋。一些很棒的人正在将注意力转移到<em>哈利·波特</em>身上。这就是为什么这是一个艰难的决定。我会在包装派对上大约87岁，但我已经说了。”</p><p>到目前为止，邓布利多（Dumbledore）在<em>哈利·波特（Harry Potter）的</em>八部主线和三个<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/fantastic-beasts"><em>神奇的野兽</em></a>前传中饰演了四位演员。理查德·哈里斯（Richard Harris）去世前在<em>巫师的石头</em>和<em>秘密商会</em>中扮演角色，后来被迈克尔·甘班（Michael Gambon）取代，剩下的六部主线电影。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/michael-gambon-dies-aged-82-3505899">甘本（Gambon）于2023年去世，享年82岁。</a></p><p>在<em>《死亡圣器》第一部分</em>和<em>第二部分</em>期间的闪回中，托比·雷博（Toby Regbo）描绘了一个年轻的邓布利多。最后，裘德·劳（Jude Law）在<em>《神奇野兽》</em>电影中描绘了一个中年的邓布利多。 </p><figure id="attachment_3811734" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3811734" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3811734" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/richard-harris-dumbledore@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/richard-harris-dumbledore@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/richard-harris-dumbledore@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/richard-harris-dumbledore@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/richard-harris-dumbledore@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/richard-harris-dumbledore@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/richard-harris-dumbledore@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3811734" class="wp-caption-text">理查德·哈里斯（Richard Harris）为邓布利多（Dumbledore）。学分：法新社/法新